aw their own conclusions as to its nature. </div><div class="t me5c x17 he ye8b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">. . . We no less than they need to learn the </div><div class="t m3d4 x17 he y897 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">foundation principles of the kingdom of </div><div class="t m1e2 x17 h21 y251 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God.&quot;-The Desire of Ages, </div><div class="t m1199 x87 he y251 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 299. </div><div class="t m1f3 x14 he y670 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t mf64 x28 he y66f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How is every disciple of Christ </div><div class="t m483 x17 he y3c0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to relate himself to trial and persecu-</div><div class="t m83c x17 he y866 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion? Matt. 5:10-12; Luke 6:22, 23. </div><div class="t mf3 x4a he y6d9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NoTE.-&quot;While the Lord has not prom-</div><div class="t ma3b x17 he y57b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ised His people exemption from trials, He </div><div class="t m39f x17 he y911 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has promised that which is far better. He </div><div class="t m1b91 x17 he y82e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has said, &apos;As thy days, so shall thy </div><div class="t m7b5 x17 he y533 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">strength be.&apos; My grace is sufficient for </div><div class="t m61c x3e he y915 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thee; for My strength is made perfect in </div><div class="t m57a x17 he y4f6 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">weakness.&apos; If you are called to go through </div><div class="t m6e x3e he yb24 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the fiery furnace for His sake, Jesus will be </div><div class="t m1e2c x3d h33 y5aa ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus Magnifies the Law </div><div class="t m1335 x7b he y463 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. What did Jesus teach concern-</div><div class="t m1a36 x7 he y913 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing the law? How serious is the vio-</div><div class="t mbea x7 he y7c5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lation of any one of the Ten Com-</div